dopustimo Oilerima da nas uhvate.

860
01:10:59,711 --> 01:11:02,059
Kada Vejk postaje prijetnja?

861
01:11:02,351 --> 01:11:03,665
Na našem trenutnom kursu,

862
01:11:04,056 --> 01:11:08,438
možemo biti u dometu njihovih
kopnenih letjelica do negde ove večeri.

863
01:11:10,940 --> 01:11:13,735
Ne osećam potrebu da
rizikujem više živote ili avione

864
01:11:14,040 --> 01:11:16,366
da potone dva teško
oštećena japanska broda.

865
01:11:16,988 --> 01:11:18,022
Slazem se.

866
01:11:19,862 --> 01:11:21,142
Ostanite na kursu brzinom

867
01:11:21,767 --> 01:11:23,413
dok ne sakupimo naše avione,

868
01:11:23,939 --> 01:11:25,548
i onda prekine našu potragu.
- Da, ser.

869
01:11:27,682 --> 01:11:28,575
Ser, možda...

870
01:11:33,663 --> 01:11:34,788
Da, ser.

871
01:11:45,493 --> 01:11:48,733
<i>A na štitu metka bila
je iscrtana zastava Japa.</i>

872
01:11:48,735 --> 01:11:50,805
<i>Šta dovraga?
- Ne, kao ubojstvo.</i>

873
01:11:50,807 --> 01:11:52,643
<i>Kao, kako piloti
slike Wildcat ubijaju</i>

874
01:11:52,645 --> 01:11:53,968
